text: Strandiata renominata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, and the type species of its genus. It was described by Vitali F. and Vitali C. in 2012. It is known from Ethiopia.BioLib.cz - Strandiata renominata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2012
